text: Wickham Wasps Rugby League Club is an Australian rugby league club from Wickham, Western Australia. They conduct teams for Juniors, Seniors and Ladies teams to compete in the Pilbara Rugby League competition. ==Notable Juniors== ==See also== *Rugby league in Western Australia ==References== ==External links== *Wickham Wasps Fox Sports pulse *Wickham Wasps Team App * Category:Rugby league teams in Western Australia Category:Rugby clubs established in 1991 Category:1991 establishments in Australia
